Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:10.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}飽きるくらい　全部キミがほしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:12.92,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ハートは涙でいっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:17.74,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}恋のいろはとかまだわかってないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:21.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}何度も繰り返すけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:23.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}寸前でまた次回へ　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:29.74,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}スイートな乙女心は　あいにく取り扱ってないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:32.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ねぇ　これがI LOVE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.58,0:01:36.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Someday I really really send it, precious for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:41.63,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Someday I really really send it, precious for you!
